Reshaping First, let&rsquo;s compute average prices by neighbourhood and date using the merged dataset.
df_long = df_merged.groupby(['neighbourhood', 'date'])['price_x'].agg('mean').reset_index() df_long.head()   .dataframe tbody tr th:only-of-type { vertical-align: middle; } .dataframe tbody tr th { vertical-align: top; } .dataframe thead th { text-align: right; }  
